71
0:03:18.16,000 --> 0:03:21,000
a good graphic invites the eye to dart around,

72
0:03:21.16,000 --> 0:03:23,000
to selectively create a visual logic.

73
0:03:23.16,000 --> 0:03:28,000
So the act of engaging, and looking at the image creates the meaning.

74
0:03:28.16,000 --> 0:03:3,000
It's the selective logic.

75
0:03:30.16,000 --> 0:03:33,000
Now we've augmented this and spatialized this information.

