80
0:03:43.16,000 --> 0:03:46,000
So the act of engaging and creating interactive imagery

81
0:03:46.16,000 --> 0:03:48,000
enriches meaning.

82
0:03:48.16,000 --> 0:03:51,000
It activates a different part of the brain.

83
0:03:51.16,000 --> 0:03:53,000
And then the limbic system

84
0:03:53.16,000 --> 0:03:56,000
is activated when we see motion, when we see color,

