87
0:04:01.16,000 --> 0:04:03,000
So the point of this is what?

88
0:04:03.16,000 --> 0:04:06,000
We make meaning by seeing,

89
0:04:06.16,000 --> 0:04:08,000
by an act of visual interrogation.

90
0:04:08.16,000 --> 0:04:1,000
The lessons for us are three-fold.

91
0:04:10.16,000 --> 0:04:14,000
First, use images to clarify what we're trying to communicate.

92
0:04:14.16,000 --> 0:04:17,000
Secondly make those images interactive

93
0:04:17.16,000 --> 0:04:19,000
so that we engage much more fully.

94
0:04:19.16,000 --> 0:04:21,000
And the third is to augment memory

95
0:04:21.16,000 --> 0:04:23,000
by creating a visual persistence.

96
